keywords: compatibility, differences, awk, bwk, mawk, gawk, jawk
description: Compatibility notes and live compatibility reports for Jawk against POSIX, BWK, and gawk test suites.

Compatibility and Compliance
=============================

<!-- MACRO{toc|fromDepth=2|toDepth=3|id=toc} -->

Jawk is checked during `mvn verify` against 3 upstream compatibility families:
[POSIX awk specifications](https://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/utilities/awk.html),
[One True Awk](https://github.com/onetrueawk/awk),
[GNU Awk](https://www.gnu.org/software/gawk/). This page summarizes what currently passes, fails, errors, or remains intentionally skipped.

